'''科特韦赫-德弗里斯数学研究所'''（{{lang-nl|Korteweg-de Vries Instituut voor Wiskunde}}，缩写为'''KdVI'''）是[[阿姆斯特丹大学|阿姆斯特丹大学]]下属的一所数学教育和研究机构。它以荷兰数学家[[迪德里克·科特韦赫|迪德里克·科特韦赫]]和[[古斯塔夫·德弗里斯|古斯塔夫·德弗里斯]]的名字命名。<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Korteweg-de Vries Institute for Mathematics|url=https://www.narcis.nl/organisation/RecordID/ORG1235559/Language/en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112003712/https://www.narcis.nl/organisation/RecordID/ORG1235559/Language/en|archive-date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-11|website=NARCIS|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Instituutsleden|url=https://www.wiskgenoot.nl/index.php?page=21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113131039/https://www.wiskgenoot.nl/index.php?page=21|archive-date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-01-11|website=wiskgenoot|language=nl|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Korteweg-de Vries Institute for Mathematics, Universiteit van Amsterdam|url=https://euro-math-soc.eu/corporate/korteweg-de-vries-institute-mathematics-universiteit-van-amsterdam|access-date=2021-01-11|work=European Mathematical Society|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225084306/https://euro-math-soc.eu/corporate/korteweg-de-vries-institute-mathematics-universiteit-van-amsterdam|dead-url=no}}</ref>

